data.name: trans_CN_Live2D
data.value: ,文件 新建模型文件,CMD_NEW_MODEL 新建动画文件,CMD_NEW_ANIMATION 打开指定文件,CMD_OPEN 打开最后一次保存关闭的文件,CMD_RECENT_FILE_OPEN 关闭当前文件,CMD_DEL_TAB_TABBOX 关闭所有文件,CMD_CLOSE_ALL 保存,CMD_SAVE 另存为…,CMD_SAVE_AS 应用模板,CMD_MODELING_TEMPLATE 打开物理/场景混合设定,CMD_SHOW_VIEWER 导出模型为图片,CMD_EXPORT_MODEL_AS_PNG 导出模型为PSD,CMD_EXPORT_MODEL_AS_PSD 导出场景为GIF,CMD_EXPORT_SCENE_AS_ANIMATED_GIF 导出场景为PNG,CMD_EXPORT_SCENE_AS_PNG 导出为moc3文件,CMD_EXPORT_EMBEDDED_MODEL 导出动态文件,CMD_EXPORT_MOTION 导出为视频,CMD_EXPORT_SCENE_AS_VIDEO 网格设定,CMD_GRID_SETTING_SPLIT_INTERVAL 键盘快捷键,CMD_KEYBOARD_SHORTCUT_SETTING 设置背景颜色,CMD_SETTING_BACKGROUND_COLOR 重设背景颜色,CMD_SETTING_RESET_BACKGROUND_COLOR 模型统计数据,CMD_MODELING_STATISTICS 画布设定,CMD_MODEL_SETTING 重设模型尺寸,CMD_RESIZE_MODEL_DOCUMENT 退出Editor,CMD_EXIT ,编辑 复原,CMD_UNDO 重做,CMD_REDO 剪切,CMD_CUT 复制,CMD_COPY 粘贴,CMD_PASTE 删除,CMD_DELETE 解除选择,CMD_ESC 全选,CMD_SELECT_ALL ,显示 显示辅助线(建模视图),CMD_SHOW_GUI_GUIDE_FOR_MODELING 显示栅格(建模视图),CMD_SHOW_GUI_GRID 辅助线设定(建模视图),CMD_SETTING_GUIDES_MODELING_SETTING 突出显示变形器的子物体,CMD_HIGH_LIGHT_DEFORMER_CHILD 显示调整弯曲变形器尺寸的子元素,CMD_SHOW_CHILD_UNDER_WARP_DEFORMER_CTRL_MODE 隐藏选择状态,CMD_HIDE_OBJECT_SELECTION 突出所选物体,CMD_FOCUS_ON_SELECTED_OBJECTS 使用模型引导图像显示模型,CMD_SHOW_MODEL_BY_RAW_IMAGE 使用纹理集显示模型,CMD_SHOW_MODEL_BY_TEXTURE_ATLAS 显示/隐藏边界框,CMD_TOGGLE_DISPLAY_BOUNDINGBOX 建模视图,CMD_PREVIEW_ONIONSKIN_MODELER 动画视图,CMD_PREVIEW_ONIONSKIN_ANIMATOR 表单动画视图,CMD_PREVIEW_ONIONSKIN_FORM_ANIMATION ,建模 创建曲面变形器,CMD_CREATE_WARP_DEFORMER 创建旋转变形器,CMD_CREATE_ROTATION_DEFORMER 选择父变形器,CMD_SELECT_PARENT_DEFORMER 删除变形器及子级,CMD_DELETE_DEFORMER_AND_CHILDREN 削除变形器并由子物体继承参数,CMD_DELETE_DEFORMER_AND_SET_PARAM 动作反转,CMD_INVERSION_OF_MOVEMENT 验证变形器,CMD_VALIDATE_DEFORMER_DIALOG 从单个图形网格生成图形路径,CMD_CREATE_ART_PATH_INDIVISUALLY 从多个图形网格生成图形路径,CMD_CREATE_ART_PATH_COLLECT 从部件为图形路径取色,CMD_PICK_ART_MESH_COLOR_FOR_ART_PATH 从部件为图形路径取透明度,CMD_PICK_ART_MESH_ALPHA_FOR_ART_PATH 估计图形路径宽度,CMD_ESTIMATE_LINE_WIDTH 选取图形路径信息,CMD_PICK_ART_MESH_LINE_INFO 校准图形路径控制点,CMD_CALIBRATE_ART_PATH_CTRL_POINT 添加控制点以与图形网格对齐,CMD_ADD_NEAR_CTRL_POINT_FOR_SELECTED_ART_MESH_COUNTER 在所有图形路径控制点的中间添加一个点,CMD_INSERT_INTER_ART_PATH_POINTS_TO_ALL 在所选图形路径控制点的中间添加一个点,CMD_INSERT_INTER_ART_PATH_POINTS_TO_SELECTED_POINTS 适应部件轮廓,CMD_FIT_ART_MESH_CONTOUR 打开自动生成图新路径对话框,CMD_OPEN_LINE_INFO_PICK_DIALOG 从图形路径创建变形路径,CMD_CREATE_CONTROLLER_EXTENSION_BY_ART_PATH 将图形网格的变形烘焙到图形路径,CMD_EDIT_MULTIKEY_FOR_ARTPATH 连接图形路径,CMD_CONNECT_ART_PATH 拆分图形路径,CMD_DISCONNECT_ART_PATH 全部跟随,CMD_BIND_ART_PATH_POINT_TO_ARTMESH_EXTENSION_TO_ALL 全部取消,CMD_UNBIND_ART_PATH_POINT_TO_ARTMESH_EXTENSION_TO_ALL 按照所选的控制点,CMD_BIND_ART_PATH_POINT_TO_ARTMESH_EXTENSION 释放所选控制点,CMD_UNBIND_ART_PATH_POINT_TO_ARTMESH_EXTENSION 加粗图形路径的控制点,CMD_EDIT_WIDTH_ART_PATH_CONTROL_POINT_THICKEN 加细图形路径的控制点,CMD_EDIT_WIDTH_ART_PATH_CONTROL_POINT_THIN 编辑纹理集,CMD_TEXTURE_ATLAS 切换显示原图和纹理集,CMD_CHANGE_ARTMESH_INPUT 将纹理集应用于原图（bete）,CMD_GENERATE_RAW_IMAGE_FROM_TEXTURE_ATLAS 四角形状合成,CMD_AUTO_BLEND_4_CORNER 重置为默认值,CMD_SET_DEFAULT_PARAMETERS 对其所选对象的参数配置,CMD_SET_SAME_PARAMETERS_TO_ALL_SELECTED 参数设置,CMD_OPEN_PARAMETER_SETTING 锁定默认的变形器,CMD_CHANGE_DEFAULT_KEYFORM_LOCKED 自动眨眼和口形同步的设定,CMD_SHOW_EFFECT_SETTING_DIALOG 扩展插值,CMD_EDIT_EXTENSION_INTERPOLATION 胶水效果开/关,CMD_GLUE_CHANGE_ENABLE 蒙皮,CMD_GLUE_SKINNING 变形路径进行蒙皮,CMD_DEFORM_PATH_SKINNING 生成旋转变形器的参数,CMD_ADD_PARAMETER_FOR_ROTATION_DEFORMER 反转,CMD_MODELING_REFLECTION 放大缩小指定倍率,CMD_RESIZE_ARTMESH_WITH_SCALE 恢复原状,CMD_RESTORE_ORIGINAL_SHAPE 复制形状,CMD_COPY_SHAPE 贴上形状,CMD_PASTE_SHAPE 混合形状,CMD_BLEND_SHAPE 放大/缩小,CMD_CREATE_FREE_DEFORM_HANDLER_AS_SCALE_MODE 旋转,CMD_CREATE_FREE_DEFORM_HANDLER_AS_ROTATE_MODE 自由变形,CMD_CREATE_FREE_DEFORM_HANDLER_AS_FREE_MODE
